reviewText: Great DVD if you like England.
The picture is faded and does not show well on the screen. I would not buy this dvd again. Not a good buy

Bought this to add to my "British Rail Journeys" collection only to find that it is the same program that was included in British Rail Journeys: Vol, 1. from another distributor which is cheaper and contains two programs.(See my review.) No reason not to buy this but be advised that it is something you may already have.
